text: Trachylepis lacertiformis, the bronze rock skink, is a species of skink found in Zimbabwe, Angola, Malawi, and Mozambique. ==References== lacertiformis Category:Reptiles of Zimbabwe Category:Reptiles of Angola Category:Reptiles of Malawi Category:Reptiles of Mozambique Category:Reptiles described in 1854 Category:Taxa named by Wilhelm Peters
title: Trachylepis lacertiformis
